---
// Quote — large editorial display quote
---

<section class="py-28 md:py-36 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-obsidian">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-8">
    <!-- Decorative mark -->
    <span
      class="font-display text-gold leading-none select-none"
      style="font-size: 5rem; line-height: 1; opacity: 0.35; font-weight: 300;"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      &ldquo;
    </span>

    <!-- Quote text -->
    <blockquote
      class="font-display text-parchment italic m-0 leading-snug text-center"
      style="font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.1rem); font-weight: 300; max-width: 780px;"
    >
      In an age of digital noise, having a private space to curate your
      intellectual foundation isn&apos;t a luxury &mdash; it&apos;s a necessity
      for high-performance thinking.
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>
